Priority: optional
Maintainer: Konstantin P. <ria.freelander@gmail.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9), cmake (>= 2.8.0), libpeas-dev (>= 1.2.0), libgtk-3-dev (>= 3.12.0), vala-panel-dev, xfce4-panel-dev (>= 4.11.2), libxfconf-0-dev
Standards-Version: 3.9.6
Homepage: https://github.com/rilian-la-te/xfce4-sntray-plugin
