Package: xfce4-sntray-plugin
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, vala-panel-sntray-common (= ${source:Version})
Recommends: sni-qt, libappindicator1, libappindicator3-1
Description: This package provides StatusNotifier plugin for xfce4-panel
 StatusNotifier is new D-Bus standard for system tray.
 It is shared both by Ubuntu Unity and KDE.
 There is several plugins for show StatusNotifiers for different DEs,
 for XFCE it is indicator-application and xfce4-snw-plugin

